rows.label: tlk45450112_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Bahn-sama has been too busy
lately to give us much work
to do, clerical or dancing.

rows.label: tlk45450112_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Since our pay is
commission-based, that's
not great for our bottom line.

rows.label: tlk45450112_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a real problem... I'm
not sure what I ought to do.
